dmca.title: Blog Posts DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google

works.description:
This user has copied my complete personal
 
blogposts including my text & photos, including my personal close {peace, 

love & hugs} Carrie
: oh clementine-my love of clementines, playing designer-my design work
for  
my friend, feature friday-feature artist my college friend Amy Perrotti,  
call me- about my phone photo includes my personal watermark, just because
 
- green apples organization & my daughter's room, if only-woodstoves & my 

ever cold studio, a problem-about my craft supply addiction. All articles 

minus one have my personal photography. This person is completely using  
these articles as their own with no links back or mention as to where they
 
are from.
